nt/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="梅根·塞·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 出席 2024 年格莱美预赛晚会暨格莱美向行业偶像致敬。图片来源：Leon Bennett/Getty Images for The Recording Academy" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-@-2000x1270-Leon-Bennett_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion</a> ) 的律师对上个月针对她提起的“耸人听闻”的工作骚扰诉讼做出了回应。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/megan-thee-stallion-cover-interview-2020-girls-in-the-hood-2700621">封面上 – Megan Thee Stallion：“我现在正在为我的王朝而努力”</a></li></ul><p>早在4月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-accused-of-harrassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-by-former-photographer-3749892">摄影师Emilio Garcia指责您种马</a>（真名梅根·皮特）和她的管理Roc国家骚扰并创造了敌对的工作环境。他声称，休斯顿说唱歌手在2022年在西班牙巡回演出时在他面前的一辆汽车上发生了性关系，并对他发表了“性和胖子的评论”。</p><p>加西亚补充说，他认为你种马和罗克国家后来通过减少工作并最终终止他来报复他。</p><p>当时，皮特的皮特的律师玛丽·亨德森（Mari Henderson）和亚历克斯·斯皮罗（Alex Spiro）在一份声明中说：“这是对金钱的就业要求 - 没有提出过性骚扰索赔，并指控试图使她尴尬。我们将在法庭上处理。” </p><figure id="attachment_3761309" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761309" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761309" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage.jpg" alt="梅根（Megan Thee）在2024年的格莱米（Grammy Gala）和格莱美（Grammy）向行业偶像致敬。图片来源：Momodu Mansaray/Wireimage" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/megan-thee-stallion-Momodu-Mansaray_WireImage-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761309" class="wp-caption-text">梅根（Megan Thee）在2024年的格莱米（Grammy Gala）和格莱美（Grammy）向行业偶像致敬。图片来源：Momodu Mansaray/Wireimage</figcaption></figure><p>在<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/megan-thee-stallion-responds-cameraman-car-sex-harassment-lawsuit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>发布的一份报告中，梅根的律师昨天（5月30日）提出了回应。亨德森（Henderson）和斯皮罗（Spiro）说，加西亚（Garcia）的诉讼“几乎完全由虚假，对事实的虚假陈述以及没有依据或法律且没有优点的古怪主张。”</p><p> Spiro继续称呼原告“一位正在操纵司法系统的骗子艺术家，以拼命的努力，以促进他失败的歌曲事业，同时试图拆除Megan Thee Stallion的成功职业。”</p><p>在报告的后期，Spiro声称这位前承包商在一再“伪造了他的发票并为他从未完成的服务伪造了他的发票，并收取了超额费用。”</p><p>律师补充说：“对这场备受瞩目的演出和他从明星的内部圈子流亡的流亡感到生气，原告在事实和法律上提出了一个琐碎的抱怨。</p><p> “原告进行了犯罪的工资和劳资纠纷，并以轰动性的虚假指控，放荡和工作场所的骚扰来胜过他的轻率主张皮特。” </p><figure id="attachment_3531147" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3531147" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3531147" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion.jpg" alt="Megan Thee Stallion（Axelle/Bauer-Griffin/Filmmagic的照片）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/megan-thee-stallion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3531147" class="wp-caption-text"> Megan Thee Stallion（Axelle/Bauer-Griffin/Filmmagic的照片）</figcaption></figure><p>您种马的律师还认为，此案是完全错误的地方提起的，现在正在寻求将其搬到联邦法院。他们说，此案“绝对与加利福尼亚州法院无关”，理由是加西亚住在德克萨斯州，而你种马居住在佛罗里达州。</p><p>亨德森和斯皮罗写道：“原告更关心在不当论坛上提起诉讼，而不是准确地辩护他的主张的事实。”</p><p> <em>Billboard</em>获得了加西亚律师罗恩·赞布拉诺（Ron Zambrano）的声明，他说梅根（Megan）从未提出过有关他伪造发票或过度收费的任何问题。他们称回应提交了“另一位名人羞辱受害者并将责备从自己的憎恶行为转移的尝试。”</p><p>桑布拉诺说：“她的律师是正确的，我们的客户很生气，但不是被所谓的流放&#39;从明星的内部圈子中流放&#39;。” “他很生气，因为他的对待方式。梅根·你种马打破了法律。时期。除了她，没有人躺在这里。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>已与Megan Thee Stallion的代表取得了联系，以评论正在进行的诉讼。 </p><figure id="attachment_3576911" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3576911" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3576911" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/megan-thee-stallion-KENA-BETANCUR_AFP-via-Getty-Images-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="梅根·泰（Megan thee）的种马（2024）纽约电影首映。图片来源：Kena Betancur/AFP通过Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/megan-thee-stallion-KENA-BETANCUR_AFP-via-Getty-Images-@-2000-x-1270