鼓手试图在慈善事业中播放Foo Fighters的整个唱片https://www.nme.com/news/music/drummer-attempts-to-play-foo-fighters-entire-discography-in-one-sitting-for-charity-3761487?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=drummer-尝试竞争狂热的战斗机 - 犯罪学院术Emma WilkesFri, 31 May 2024 21:18:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3761487 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·霍金斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格雷格·巴顿（Greg Barton）将总共播放128首歌曲，这将需要9个半小时</p><p>邮政鼓手试图在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drummer-attempts-to-play-foo-fighters-entire-discography-in-one-sitting-for-charity-3761487">在慈善机构中，试图打Foo Fighter的整个唱片</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·霍金斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/taylor-hawkins-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>鼓手格雷格·巴顿（Greg Barton）将通过播放曾经为慈善机构坐下来创作的每首<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>歌曲而成为“ FOO斗争癌症”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/taylor-hawkins-1972-2022-foo-fighters-obituary-tribute-3190854">泰勒·霍金斯（Taylor Hawkins），1972  -  2022年：Foo Fighters Drummer，总是偷了演出</a></strong></li></ul><p>巴顿将于6月7日在128首歌曲中鼓吹，以纪念他的祖母（患有癌症）。他还向已故的Foo战士鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-hawkins">泰勒·霍金斯（Taylor Hawkins）</a>致敬，后者于2022年去世。</p><p>总的来说，巴顿将玩9个半小时，并计划在不停止的情况下进行。他已经准备好几个月了，将每个Foo Fighters Drum Track与AI隔离开来，以改善他的练习课程。</p><p> “在你说，&#39;这是不可能的，&#39;我上个月做了六个小时的比赛，并有信心我可以走！”他说。</p><p>该活动将进行直播，所有收益将捐赠给癌症研究所。您可以<a href="https://streamlabscharity.com/@gbdrummin/foo-fighting-cancer-drumming-128-foo-fighters-songs-nonstop" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>捐赠给Barton的筹款页面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7b_GqkuSyE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" vie